  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.8">
<l>karutti ṟēvu mellāp poruḷum</l>
<l>varuttitta māyap pirāṉaiyaṉṟi yārē</l>
<l>tiruttit tiṇṇilai mūvulakun taṉṉu</l>
<l>ḷiruttik kākku miyalvi ṉārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for the illusive lord who made grow</l>
<l>by [his] intention the gods and all things, who</l>
<l>is of the nature to perfectly create [and] guard</l>
<l>inside himself the three world of solid state?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
